OL,3,CPeople 'glamourise' migrant hotels,
OL,4,Crefugee tells ITV News
OL,6,FWarning: This piece includes mentions
OL,7,Fof suicide.
OL,9,FSami Gichki was in the asylum system
OL,10,Ffor 12 and a half years. He initially
OL,11,Ftravelled from Balochistan in Pakistan
OL,12,Fto the UK aged ten with his parents.
OL,14,FWhile he only spent a month in hotel
OL,15,Faccommodation in 2013, he sympathises
OL,16,Fwith people who are now spending long
OL,17,Fstints in temporary conditions.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/21
