OL,3,CPeople 'glamourise' migrant hotels,
OL,4,Crefugee tells ITV News
OL,6,F"I think often people glamourise the
OL,7,Ffact that asylum seekers are living in
OL,8,Fhotels, but it's not the same sense as
OL,9,Fin a hotel you go to when you're going
OL,10,Fon holiday," he said.
OL,12,F"You are restricted, there are curfews
OL,13,Faround what time you can be in, what
OL,14,Ftime you can go out, what people can
OL,15,Factually visit you, about what you eat.
OL,17,F"It's basically just sitting there
OL,18,Flike a sitting duck, waiting for the
OL,19,FHome Office to give you status."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/21
