OL,3,CPeople 'glamourise' migrant hotels,
OL,4,Crefugee tells ITV News
OL,6,FThe number of asylum seekers living in
OL,7,FUK hotels has risen by 8% under
OL,8,FLabour, compared to the same point
OL,9,Flast year, despite falling slightly
OL,10,Fsince March 2025, according to Home
OL,11,FOffice figures.
OL,13,FThe data is part of the usual
OL,14,Fquarterly immigration statistics and
OL,15,Fcovers Labour's first year in office.
OL,16,FIt shows 32,059 asylum seekers were in
OL,17,FUK hotels by the end of June.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/21
