OL,3,CPeople 'glamourise' migrant hotels,
OL,4,Crefugee tells ITV News
OL,6,FThe new figures come days after a
OL,7,Fcourt ruled that more than 100 asylum
OL,8,Fseekers staying at a hotel in Essex
OL,9,Fshould be removed after the local
OL,10,Fcouncil brought a legal case.
OL,12,F"I think as a society we have become
OL,13,Fso polarised," Sami told ITV News.
OL,15,F"So when I see in the news things
OL,16,Faround the Epping Hotel and the court
OL,17,Fsaying that asylum seekers should not
OL,18,Fbe housed there, my initial thoughts
OL,19,Fare, yes, I agree they should not be
OL,20,Fhoused there.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/21
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
