OL,3,CPeople 'glamourise' migrant hotels,
OL,4,Crefugee tells ITV News
OL,6,F"They should be housed in permanent
OL,7,Fhousing with agency and be able to
OL,8,Frebuild their lives in a way that is
OL,9,Fmeaningful for them, but also gives
OL,10,Fthem that sense of dignity and purpose
OL,11,Fand respect that.
OL,13,F"These places can be quite isolating
OL,14,Fand they're very disconnected from
OL,15,Fservices or places.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/21
