OL,3,CPeople 'glamourise' migrant hotels,
OL,4,Crefugee tells ITV News
OL,6,F"For example, they don't have access
OL,7,Fto medical healthcare properly because
OL,8,Fof the inability to access a GP,
OL,9,Fbecause of not having a permanent
OL,10,Faddress, not being able to go to
OL,11,Fschools in the same way that most
OL,12,Fpeople do, just because of not having
OL,13,Faccess to a permanent address.
OL,15,F"Things like this become real barriers
OL,16,Fto people and their livelihoods."
OL,18,F'I ended up being quite suicidal'
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/21
