OL,3,CPeople 'glamourise' migrant hotels,
OL,4,Crefugee tells ITV News
OL,6,FSami went to school until he was 18,
OL,7,Fbut then would have needed
OL,8,Fscholarships to go to university. This
OL,9,Fleft him unable to work but also
OL,10,Funable to study, which had a huge
OL,11,Fimpact on his mental health.
OL,13,F"I was in the state where after sixth
OL,14,Fform, I really struggled with my
OL,15,Fmental health, ended up in the space
OL,16,Fwhere I didn't really want to be here,
OL,17,Fand I ended up being quite suicidal
OL,18,Funtil I started getting support after
OL,19,Fa year and a half through mental
OL,20,Fhealth services," he said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/21
