OL,3,CPeople 'glamourise' migrant hotels,
OL,4,Crefugee tells ITV News
OL,6,FIt was only when he ended up in A&E
OL,7,Fthat he was able to get support.
OL,9,FHe was pointed towards Manchester
OL,10,FCathedral and a running charity, both
OL,11,Fof which helped him - he then ran in
OL,12,Fthe London Marathon on his 20th
OL,13,Fbirthday.
OL,15,FSami has said that his good English
OL,16,Fhas helped his progress through the
OL,17,Fasylum system - even though it has
OL,18,Fstill been very long.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/21
