OL,3,CPeople 'glamourise' migrant hotels,
OL,4,Crefugee tells ITV News
OL,6,F"The judgement that comes from being
OL,7,Fin an asylum process is... decreased
OL,8,Fby a large scale. If someone does not
OL,9,Fspeak English... I have seen how
OL,10,Fpeople are treated completely
OL,11,Fdifferently in my circumstances," he
OL,12,Fsaid.
OL,14,FBut ultimately, Sami says it is the
OL,15,F"imbalance of power" that really
OL,16,Faffects people arriving in the UK.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/21
