OL,3,CPeople 'glamourise' migrant hotels,
OL,4,Crefugee tells ITV News
OL,6,F"Even though there might not be direct
OL,7,Fconsequences for some seekers and
OL,8,Frefugees, I think just being in the
OL,9,Fsystem and waiting for so long and
OL,10,Fthat uncertainty can really affect you
OL,11,Fand impact your mental health like it
OL,12,Fdid for me," he said.
OL,14,FSami eventually got refugee status
OL,15,Fearlier this year - he separated his
OL,16,Fclaim from his family's and is allowed
OL,17,Fto stay in the UK because of his
OL,18,Fsexuality and the risk of political
OL,19,Fpersecution if he was forced to return
OL,20,Fto Pakistan.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/21
