OL,6,F'Everything fell apart'
OL,8,FAbdul has been in the UK for just over
OL,9,Fthree years after travelling from
OL,10,FSierra Leone in 2023. He is staying in
OL,11,Fshared accommodation in Stockton
OL,12,Fprovided by the Home Office.
OL,14,FHe has been there for around a year
OL,15,Fand said he had previously been living
OL,16,Felsewhere but was moved because of
OL,17,Ffaults with the building.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/21
