OL,3,CPeople 'glamourise' migrant hotels,
OL,4,Crefugee tells ITV News
OL,6,FAbdul is not allowed to work because
OL,7,Fhe does not have a permit. He said
OL,8,Fthis was because of difficulties with
OL,9,Fhis solicitor.
OL,11,F"Everything fell apart," he said.
OL,13,F"I don't like wasting time without
OL,14,Fcreating anything within yourself, the
OL,15,Fcommunity, the country."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/21
