OL,3,CPeople 'glamourise' migrant hotels,
OL,4,Crefugee tells ITV News
OL,6,FBack in Sierra Leone he had lots of
OL,7,Fareas of expertise - football,
OL,8,Frefereeing and athletics coaching, as
OL,9,Fwell as basic knowledge of
OL,10,Fconstruction, and health and social
OL,11,Fcare.
OL,13,F"With all this knowledge, sitting on
OL,14,Fthe couch, without getting any form of
OL,15,Fjob... It's really, really
OL,16,Fdevastating," he said.
OL,18,FWhile he is not allowed to work he is
OL,19,Fdependent on the money he receives
OL,20,Ffrom the Home Office every week.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/21
