OL,3,CPeople 'glamourise' migrant hotels,
OL,4,Crefugee tells ITV News
OL,6,FIn the meantime, he is trying to make
OL,7,Fthe most of his time.
OL,9,FHe described voluntary coaching as his
OL,10,F"backbone" now, as it is the only
OL,11,Fthing he still does that he used to do
OL,12,Fat home.
OL,14,F"There are so many volunteering
OL,15,Factivities that I've been doing now
OL,16,Fbecause that's the only thing that
OL,17,Fwill do to let me... reclaim myself.
OL,18,FTo increase value, to create more
OL,19,Fimpact within the community."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/21
