OL,3,CPeople 'glamourise' migrant hotels,
OL,4,Crefugee tells ITV News
OL,6,F"For my name to be written within the
OL,7,Fcommunity - I want to feel proud of
OL,8,Fthat," he added.
OL,10,FAbdul won an award last year for his
OL,11,Fvolunteering work in the community. It
OL,12,Frecognised his horticulture work in
OL,13,Fthe area as well as his sports
OL,14,Fcoaching efforts.
OL,16,F"That was one of the greatest
OL,17,Fachievements... I'm happy I got that
OL,18,Fachievement because it's within the
OL,19,Fcommunity and based on what I have
OL,20,Fdoing the community," he said.
