OL,6,FAbdul has no idea how long he might
OL,7,Fspend in his current accommodation and
OL,8,Fdoes not know how long his asylum
OL,9,Fseeker process will take.
OL,11,F'You feel sad and discouraged'
OL,13,FAnti-immigration protests have erupted
OL,14,Facross England, typically in areas
OL,15,Fthat house asylum seekers in hotels.
OL,17,FAbdul said those protests have an
OL,18,Fimpact on asylum seekers.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G16/21
