OL,3,CPeople 'glamourise' migrant hotels,
OL,4,Crefugee tells ITV News
OL,6,F"Of course protests... on that issue
OL,7,Fare not normally friendly ... All this
OL,8,Fprotesting is not good within the
OL,9,Fcommunity ... Protesting has some, let
OL,10,Fme say, negative response on the
OL,11,Findividual," he said.
OL,13,F"You feel sad, you feel a little bit
OL,14,Fdiscouraged based on the situation,"
OL,15,Fhe added.
OL,17,FHe asked people to "pardon" those who
OL,18,Flive in accommodation provided by the
OL,19,FHome Office.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G17/21
